# Netty epoll transport DoS via RST on half-closed TCP connection. Fixed only
# in Netty 4.2.13.Final; the 4.1.x line has no patch. Pathling cannot move to
# 4.2.x because Spark and Spring Boot's BOMs still pin the 4.1.x line. The
# Linux epoll transport is used by Netty-based clients/servers in Spark
# internals; Pathling does not expose Netty servers on its public HTTP path.
CVE-2026-42577

